name: AVCaptureSession.Preset
desc: Constants to define capture setting presets using the sessionPreset property.

items.name: static let low: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for output video and audio bit rates suitable for sharing over 3G.

items.name: static let medium: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for output video and audio bit rates suitable for sharing over WiFi.

items.name: static let high: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for high-quality video and audio output.

items.name: static let photo: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for high-resolution photo quality output.

items.name: static let inputPriority: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies that the capture session does not control audio and video output settings.

items.name: static let qHD960x540: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for quarter HD quality (960 x 540 pixel) video output.

items.name: static let hd1280x720: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for 720p quality (1280 x 720 pixel) video output.

items.name: static let hd1920x1080: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Capture settings suitable for 1080p-quality (1920 x 1080 pixels) video output.

items.name: static let hd4K3840x2160: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Capture settings suitable for 2160p-quality (3840 x 2160 pixels) video output.

items.name: static let iFrame960x540: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings to achieve 960 x 540 quality iFrame H.264 video at about 30 Mbits/sec with AAC audio.

items.name: static let iFrame1280x720: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings to achieve 1280 x 720 quality iFrame H.264 video at about 40 Mbits/sec with AAC audio.

items.name: static let qvga320x240: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for 320 x 240 pixel video output.

items.name: static let vga640x480: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for VGA quality (640 x 480 pixel) video output.

items.name: static let cif352x288: AVCaptureSession.Preset
items.desc: Specifies capture settings suitable for CIF quality (352 x 288 pixel) video output.

items.name: init(rawValue: String)
items.desc: Creates a preset from its raw string value.
